<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">William Robertson Davies</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:RobertsonDavies.jpg" class="image" title="RobertsonDavies.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/17/RobertsonDavies.jpg/200px-RobertsonDavies.jpg" width="200" height="201" border="0" /></a><br />
